  <entry>
    <title>difyTool模块解析</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/30/difyTool%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/30/difyTool%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Dify-Tools-模块架构详解"><a href="#Dify-Tools-模块架构详解" class="headerlink" title="Dify Tools 模块架构详解"></a>Dify Tools 模块架构详解</h1><h2 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h2><p>Dify 的 Tools 模块采用<strong>三层流程架构</strong>设计，实现了从参数接收、工具决策到最终执行的完整生命周期管理。该架构通过职责分离，确保了工具调用的灵活性、可扩展性和可观测性。</p><hr><h2 id="第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）"><a href="#第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）" class="headerlink" title="第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）"></a>第一层：组装与决策层（ToolManage）</h2><h3 id="核心职责"><a href="#核心职责" class="headerlink" title="核心职责"></a>核心职责</h3><p>ToolManage 作为工具的<strong>入口调度器</strong>，负责接收外部参数、决策工具路由、组装完整工具实例。</p><h3 id="执行流程"><a href="#执行流程" class="headerlink" title="执行流程"></a>执行流程</h3><pre><code class="mermaid">flowchart TD    A[外部参数传入] --> B[ToolManage接收]    B --> C[调用 get_tool_runtime]    C --> D[确定 Provider]    C --> E[获取 Runtime 模块]    E --> F[参数补充与信息完善]    D --> G[获取具体 Tool 定义]    F --> H[组装 Runtime + Tools]    G --> H    H --> I[生成完整工具实例]    I --> J[交付给 ToolEngine]</code></pre><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">get_credentials_schema</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token builtin">list</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>ProviderConfig<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""        returns the credentials schema of the provider        :return: the credentials schema        """</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> deepcopy<span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>credentials_schema<span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token decorator annotation punctuation">@abstractmethod</span>    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">get_tool</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool_name<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Tool<span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""        returns a tool that the provider can provide        :return: tool        """</span>        <span class="token keyword">pass</span>    <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">validate_credentials_format</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> credentials<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>这个provider的作用就是获得供应商的信息，同时返回tool实例，我们通过供应商返回的信息进行验证和前端渲染表单</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">from</span> typing <span class="token keyword">import</span> Any<span class="token keyword">from</span> pydantic <span class="token keyword">import</span> BaseModel<span class="token punctuation">,</span> Field<span class="token keyword">from</span> core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>app<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entities<span class="token punctuation">.</span>app_invoke_entities <span class="token keyword">import</span> InvokeFrom<span class="token keyword">from</span> core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plugin<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entities<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plugin_daemon <span class="token keyword">import</span> CredentialType<span class="token keyword">from</span> core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>tools<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entities<span class="token punctuation">.</span>tool_entities <span class="token keyword">import</span> ToolInvokeFrom<span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">ToolRuntime</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>BaseModel<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""    Meta data of a tool call processing    """</span>    tenant_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span>  <span class="token comment"># 租户ID - 标识当前工作空间/组织，用于权限隔离和数据隔离</span>    tool_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token comment"># 工具标识 - 具体调用的工具ID</span>    invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">:</span> InvokeFrom <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token comment"># 调用来源 - 标识从何处触发（如 Debugger、WebApp、ServiceAPI 等）</span>    tool_invoke_from<span class="token punctuation">:</span> ToolInvokeFrom <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token comment"># 工具调用来源 - 区分是 Agent 调用、Workflow 调用还是直接调用</span>    credentials<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> Field<span class="token punctuation">(</span>default_factory<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment"># 凭证信息 - 存储 API Key、Token 等敏感认证信息</span>    credential_type<span class="token punctuation">:</span> CredentialType <span class="token operator">=</span> Field<span class="token punctuation">(</span>default<span class="token operator">=</span>CredentialType<span class="token punctuation">.</span>API_KEY<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment"># 凭证类型 - 如 API_KEY、OAUTH2 等</span>    runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> Field<span class="token punctuation">(</span>default_factory<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment"># 运行时参数 - 动态传入的额外配置参数</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>runtime用来存储工具执行所需的所有上下文信息，这些信息是保证后续能够运行的必要参数</p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="language-python">def get_tool_runtime(        cls,        provider_type: ToolProviderType,        provider_id: str,        tool_name: str,        tenant_id: str,        invoke_from: InvokeFrom = InvokeFrom.DEBUGGER,        tool_invoke_from: ToolInvokeFrom = ToolInvokeFrom.AGENT,        credential_id: str | None = None,    ) -&gt; Union[BuiltinTool, PluginTool, ApiTool, WorkflowTool, MCPTool]:<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">get_tool_runtime这个函数接受provider的类型和工具的名字，以此来确定到底要调用哪个provider&#96;&#96;&#96;&#96;pythonif provider_type &#x3D;&#x3D; ToolProviderType.BUILT_IN:    # 获取 Provider    provider_controller &#x3D; cls.get_builtin_provider(provider_id, tenant_id)    # 获取 Tool（无 runtime）    builtin_tool &#x3D; provider_controller.get_tool(tool_name)    # 查询数据库获取凭证配置    builtin_provider &#x3D; (        db.session.query(BuiltinToolProvider)        .where(            BuiltinToolProvider.tenant_id &#x3D;&#x3D; tenant_id,            BuiltinToolProvider.provider &#x3D;&#x3D; provider_id        )        .order_by(BuiltinToolProvider.is_default.desc())        .first()    )    # ...中间的验证代码    # 构建 ToolRuntime（核心！）    runtime &#x3D; ToolRuntime(        tenant_id&#x3D;tenant_id,        credentials&#x3D;dict(decrypted_credentials),           # 解密后的凭证        credential_type&#x3D;CredentialType.of(builtin_provider.credential_type),        runtime_parameters&#x3D;&#123;&#125;,                              # 运行时参数        invoke_from&#x3D;invoke_from,        tool_invoke_from&#x3D;tool_invoke_from,    )        # 组装并返回（核心！）    return builtin_tool.fork_tool_runtime(runtime&#x3D;runtime)<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>我们获取到provider和tools之后，就构建ToolRuntime，然后通过fork方法合并成新的tool,最后就把这个交给ToolEngine### 关键能力| 能力          | 说明                                    || ----------- | ------------------------------------- || Provider 决策 | 通过 get\_tool\_runtime() 动态决定要调用的服务提供商 || 参数补充        | 调用 Runtime 模块获取额外上下文信息，完善调用参数         || 实例组装        | 将 Runtime 配置与 Tool 定义融合，构建可执行的工具实例    |***## 第二层：执行引擎层（ToolEngine）### 核心职责ToolEngine 是具体执行层，负责工具的生命周期管理、前端通信、执行监控和数据持久化。### 执行流程详解#### 1. 入口方法：agent\_invoke （对话格式）<figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">agent_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool_instance<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment"># 1. 通知前端 - 执行开始</span>    self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_notify_frontend<span class="token punctuation">(</span>status<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"started"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 2. 进入实际执行逻辑</span>    result <span class="token operator">=</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_instance<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># 3. 后续处理...</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> result<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>#### 如果是工作流： generic_invoke#### 如果是工作流： generic_invoke<figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">generic_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>        tool<span class="token punctuation">:</span> Tool<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        user_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">:</span> DifyWorkflowCallbackHandler<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        workflow_call_depth<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">int</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        app_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        message_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Generator<span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token triple-quoted-string string">"""        Workflow invokes the tool with the given arguments.        """</span>        <span class="token keyword">try</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>            <span class="token comment"># hit the callback handler</span>            workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">.</span>on_tool_start<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_name<span class="token operator">=</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>identity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool_inputs<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token builtin">isinstance</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> WorkflowTool<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>  <span class="token comment">#控制深度，防止死循环</span>                tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>workflow_call_depth <span class="token operator">=</span> workflow_call_depth <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token number">1</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime <span class="token keyword">and</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token comment"># 合并参数</span>                tool_parameters <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token operator">**</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">**</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>            response <span class="token operator">=</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>                user_id<span class="token operator">=</span>user_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                tool_parameters<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                conversation_id<span class="token operator">=</span>conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                app_id<span class="token operator">=</span>app_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                message_id<span class="token operator">=</span>message_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            <span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token comment"># hit the callback handler</span>            response <span class="token operator">=</span> workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">.</span>on_tool_execution<span class="token punctuation">(</span>                tool_name<span class="token operator">=</span>tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>entity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>identity<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                tool_inputs<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span>                tool_outputs<span class="token operator">=</span>response<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            <span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> response        <span class="token keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="token keyword">as</span> e<span class="token punctuation">:</span>            workflow_tool_callback<span class="token punctuation">.</span>on_tool_error<span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span>            <span class="token keyword">raise</span> e<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>**关键动作：**- 立即通知前端执行状态变更（开始执行）- 委托 \_invoke 进行实际工具调用- 如果是工作流的话，会进行参数的合并#### 2. 核心执行：\_invoke 方法<figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">,</span> parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token comment"># 1. 记录执行开始时间</span>    start_time <span class="token operator">=</span> time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>time<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">try</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token comment"># 2. 调用 Tools.invoke 进入工具具体执行</span>        result <span class="token operator">=</span> tool<span class="token punctuation">.</span>invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token comment"># 3. 计算执行耗时</span>        duration <span class="token operator">=</span> time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>time<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span> start_time                <span class="token comment"># 4. 消息处理与数据持久化</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_process_and_save<span class="token punctuation">(</span>result<span class="token punctuation">,</span> duration<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token comment"># 5. 通知前端执行完成</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_notify_frontend<span class="token punctuation">(</span>status<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"completed"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token keyword">return</span> result    <span class="token keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="token keyword">as</span> e<span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token comment"># 异常处理</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_notify_frontend<span class="token punctuation">(</span>status<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"failed"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> error<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>e<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token keyword">raise</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>在这个逻辑里面，我们真正的开始调用tool去执行任务了，所以我们需要记录执行的耗时，同时向下传递，进入Tool的执行逻辑## 第三层：工具实现层（Tools）### 核心职责Tools 层是具体业务逻辑层，负责参数处理、类型转换和实际业务执行。### 执行流程<pre><code class="mermaid">flowchart TD    A[调用 invoke] --> B[合并 Runtime 参数]    B --> C[执行类型转换]    C --> D[调用子类._invoke]    D --> E[执行具体业务逻辑]    E --> F[返回执行结果]    F --> G[返回标准化结果]</code></pre>### 详细步骤| 步骤 | 方法           | 职责                                    || -- | ------------ | ------------------------------------- || 1  | Tools.invoke | 参数合并：将 Runtime 中的配置参数与用户传入参数融合        || 2  | Tools.invoke | 类型转换：确保参数类型符合工具定义要求（如字符串转整数、JSON 解析等） || 3  | 子类.\_invoke  | 业务执行：具体工具的实现逻辑（如调用外部 API、执行代码、查询数据库等） || 4  | Tools.invoke | 结果返回：将子类结果标准化后返回上层                    |***<figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>        self<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        user_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        app_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        message_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> Generator<span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime <span class="token keyword">and</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span>            tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">.</span>update<span class="token punctuation">(</span>self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime<span class="token punctuation">.</span>runtime_parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        <span class="token comment"># try parse tool parameters into the correct type</span>        tool_parameters <span class="token operator">=</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_transform_tool_parameters_type<span class="token punctuation">(</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">)</span>        result <span class="token operator">=</span> self<span class="token punctuation">.</span>_invoke<span class="token punctuation">(</span>            user_id<span class="token operator">=</span>user_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            tool_parameters<span class="token operator">=</span>tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            conversation_id<span class="token operator">=</span>conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            app_id<span class="token operator">=</span>app_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>            message_id<span class="token operator">=</span>message_id<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>invoke函数会检查是否有runtime参数，如果有，和tool_parameters合并，而且是tool_parameters优先，然后我们调用子类的具体实现方法：<figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token decorator annotation punctuation">@abstractmethod</span><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">_invoke</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    self<span class="token punctuation">,</span>    user_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    tool_parameters<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">dict</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token builtin">str</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> Any<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    conversation_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    app_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    message_id<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token builtin">str</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> ToolInvokeMessage <span class="token operator">|</span> <span class="token builtin">list</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">|</span> Generator<span class="token punctuation">[</span>ToolInvokeMessage<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">None</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">pass</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>抽象类，具体交给tool的子类执行## 完整数据流图<pre><code class="mermaid">flowchart TD    %% 外部请求参数    A[外部请求参数] --> B        %% 第一层：ToolManage    subgraph B["【第一层】ToolManage（组装与决策层）"]        direction TB        B1[get_tool_runtime] --> B2[确定 Provider + 获取 Runtime]        B3[调用 Runtime 模块] --> B4[补充参数信息]        B5[获取 Tool 定义] --> B6[明确工具结构]        B2 --> B7[组装 Runtime + Tools]        B4 --> B7        B6 --> B7        B7 --> B8[生成完整工具实例]    end        B --> C        %% 第二层：ToolEngine    subgraph C["【第二层】ToolEngine（执行引擎层）"]        direction TB        C1[agent_invoke] --> C2[通知前端：执行开始]        C1 --> C3[_invoke]        C3 --> C4[记录开始时间]        C3 --> C5[调用 Tools.invoke]        C3 --> C6[接收返回结果]        C3 --> C7[转化为文件格式]        C3 --> C8[写入数据库（持久化）]        C3 --> C9[通知前端：执行结束]        C3 --> C10[返回结果给上层]    end        C --> D        %% 第三层：Tools    subgraph D["【第三层】Tools（工具实现层）"]        direction TB        D1[invoke] --> D2[合并 Runtime 参数到调用参数]        D1 --> D3[参数类型转换与校验]        D1 --> D4[调用子类._invoke]        D4 --> D5[子类实现：调用外部服务/执行逻辑/计算等]        D1 --> D6[返回标准化结果]    end</code></pre>***## 架构设计亮点### 1. 职责分离（Separation of Concerns）- **ToolManage**：专注决策与组装，无执行逻辑- **ToolEngine**：专注生命周期与基础设施，无业务逻辑- **Tools**：专注业务实现，无调度逻辑### 2. 可观测性（Observability）- **前端实时通知**：执行开始/结束状态同步- **性能指标**：执行时间记录- **数据持久化**：执行结果自动存档### 3. 扩展性（Extensibility）- **新工具接入**：只需实现 子类.\_invoke- **新 Provider 支持**：ToolManage 动态决策- **参数处理**：统一的类型转换机制### 4. 容错设计- **分层异常捕获**：每层可独立处理异常- **数据持久化**：即使前端断开，执行记录依然保存- **超时控制**：Engine 层可监控执行时长***## 典型调用时序<pre><code class="mermaid">sequenceDiagram    participant 前端    participant ToolManage    participant ToolEngine    participant Tools    participant 外部服务    participant 数据库    前端->>ToolManage: 调用工具    ToolManage->>ToolEngine: 决策/组装    ToolEngine->>前端: 开始通知    Note right of 前端: 前端展示    ToolEngine->>Tools: 调用    Tools->>Tools: 参数处理    Tools->>外部服务: 调用    activate 外部服务    Note right of 外部服务: 执行    外部服务-->>Tools: 返回    deactivate 外部服务    Tools->>Tools: 结果处理    Tools-->>ToolEngine: 返回    ToolEngine->>数据库: 持久化    ToolEngine->>前端: 结束通知    Note right of 前端: 前端更新    ToolEngine-->>前端: 返回结果</code></pre></code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
    
